2. Steps to Generate App Bundles and APKs (Flutter)
Run these commands in the terminal from your project root:

To generate APK:
flutter build apk --release

To generate App Bundle (recommended for Play Store):
flutter build appbundle --release

These generate files in the build/app/outputs/flutter-apk/ or build/app/outputs/bundle/ folders.

For iOS:

To build for release (on macOS):
flutter build ios --release

Then open the .xcworkspace in Xcode → Archive → Distribute App.